ðŸ“… 2. How do delay times vary by bus company and borough?

![Delay Times - Screenshot 1](https://github.com/Zexelle/Bus-Breakdowns-and-Delays-NYC/blob/main/Delay%20Times%20-%20Screenshot%201.png)

Summary/Conclusions:

The chart above displays the 10 bus companies that have the highest average delay or breakdown time.
Recommendation: Use this to compare to # of delays, boros, and total number of trips.

Could be mechanical issues - fix with regular maintenance OR we need to fire them.

.
